window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Tad has learned more about his past, but he still doesn't know if one side or the other would imprison or kill him simply for existing. Those who know more refuse to tell him more, but share his concerns.</p> <p>Now though, it's time to move forward. He may not know what it means to be a fey but his goal remains the same, namely to open a shop and sell magical items.</p> <p>To get there though, he has a dungeon to master, errant nobles to defy, and the Lawgiver's gaze to avoid.</p> <p>Chaos is in his blood, and he's certain to bring it wherever he goes.</p>"; 
